#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.cluster.k_means.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.cluster.k\\_means"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:1 of
msgid "K-means clustering algorithm."
msgstr "K-means 聚类算法。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.cluster.k_means.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:3 of
msgid ""
"The observations to cluster. It must be noted that the data will be "
"converted to C ordering, which will cause a memory copy if the given data"
" is not C-contiguous."
msgstr ""
"要聚类的观测数据。需要注意的是数据将被转换为 C 顺序存储，如果给定数据不是"
" C 连续的，则会导致内存拷贝。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:7 of
msgid ""
"The number of clusters to form as well as the number of centroids to "
"generate."
msgstr "要形成的聚类数，也是要生成的质心数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:10 of
msgid ""
"The weights for each observation in X. If None, all observations are "
"assigned equal weight (default: None)"
msgstr ""
"X 中每个观测值的权重。如果为 None，则所有观测值被分配相等权重（默认：None"
"）。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:13 of
msgid ""
"Method for initialization, default to 'k-means||':  'k-means++' : selects"
" initial cluster centers for k-mean clustering in a smart way to speed up"
" convergence. See section Notes in k_init for more details.  'k-means||':"
" scalable k-means++.  'random': choose k observations (rows) at random "
"from data for the initial centroids.  If an ndarray is passed, it should "
"be of shape (n_clusters, n_features) and gives the initial centers.  If a"
" callable is passed, it should take arguments X, k and and a random state"
" and return an initialization."
msgstr ""
"初始化方法，默认为 'k-means||'：'k-means++'：以一种智能的方式选择 k-means"
" 聚类的初始聚类中心，以加快收敛速度。详见 k_init 中的 Notes 部分。'k-"
"means||'：可扩展的 k-means++。'random'：从数据中随机选择 k 个观测值（行）"
"作为初始质心。如果传入的是一个 ndarray，其形状应为 (n_clusters, n_"
"features)，并给出初始中心。如果传入的是一个可调用对象，则该对象应该接受"
"参数 X、k 和随机状态，并返回一个初始化结果。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:13 of
msgid "Method for initialization, default to 'k-means||':"
msgstr "初始化方法，默认为 'k-means||'："

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:15 of
msgid ""
"'k-means++' : selects initial cluster centers for k-mean clustering in a "
"smart way to speed up convergence. See section Notes in k_init for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"'k-means++' : 以智能方式选择 k-均值聚类的初始聚类中心以加速收敛。更多"
"详细信息请参见 k_init 中的 Notes 部分。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:19 of
msgid "'k-means||': scalable k-means++."
msgstr "'k-means||'：可扩展的 k-means++。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:21 of
msgid ""
"'random': choose k observations (rows) at random from data for the "
"initial centroids."
msgstr "'random'：从数据中随机选择 k 个观测值（行）作为初始质心。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:24 of
msgid ""
"If an ndarray is passed, it should be of shape (n_clusters, n_features) "
"and gives the initial centers."
msgstr "如果传入 ndarray，其形状应为 (n_clusters, n_features) 并给出初始中心。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:27 of
msgid ""
"If a callable is passed, it should take arguments X, k and and a random "
"state and return an initialization."
msgstr "如果传入可调用对象，它应该接受参数 X、k 和随机状态并返回一个初始化结果。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:30 of
msgid ""
"Number of time the k-means algorithm will be run with different centroid "
"seeds. The final results will be the best output of n_init consecutive "
"runs in terms of inertia."
msgstr ""
"k-means 算法将以不同质心种子运行的次数。最终结果将是 n_init 次连续运行中"
"惯性最小的最佳输出。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:34 of
msgid "Maximum number of iterations of the k-means algorithm to run."
msgstr "k-means 算法运行的最大迭代次数。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:36 of
msgid "Verbosity mode."
msgstr "详细模式。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:38 of
msgid "The relative increment in the results before declaring convergence."
msgstr "在宣告收敛之前结果的相对增量。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:40 of
msgid ""
"Determines random number generation for centroid initialization. Use an "
"int to make the randomness deterministic. See :term:`Glossary "
"<random_state>`."
msgstr ""
"确定质心初始化的随机数生成方式。使用整数可使随机性变为确定性的。参见 :"
"term:`Glossary <random_state>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:44 of
msgid ""
"When pre-computing distances it is more numerically accurate to center "
"the data first.  If copy_x is True (default), then the original data is "
"not modified, ensuring X is C-contiguous.  If False, the original data is"
" modified, and put back before the function returns, but small numerical "
"differences may be introduced by subtracting and then adding the data "
"mean, in this case it will also not ensure that data is C-contiguous "
"which may cause a significant slowdown."
msgstr ""
"在预先计算距离时，先对数据进行中心化处理会更加数值稳定。如果 copy_x 为 "
"True（默认），则原始数据不会被修改，确保 X 是 C 连续的。如果为 False，则"
"原始数据会被修改，并在函数返回前恢复，但通过减去并加回数据均值可能会引入"
"微小的数值差异，在这种情况下也不能保证数据是 C 连续的，从而可能导致显著的"
"性能下降。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:52 of
msgid ""
"K-means algorithm to use. The classical EM-style algorithm is \"full\". "
"The \"elkan\" variation is more efficient by using the triangle "
"inequality, but currently doesn't support sparse data. \"auto\" chooses "
"\"elkan\" for dense data and \"full\" for sparse data."
msgstr ""
"使用的 K-means 算法。经典的 EM 风格算法是 \"full\"。\"elkan\" 变体通过"
"使用三角不等式更为高效，但目前不支持稀疏数据。\"auto\" 会在密集数据时选择"
" \"elkan\"，而在稀疏数据时选择 \"full\"。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:57 of
msgid "Only work for kmeans||, used in each iteration in kmeans||."
msgstr "仅适用于 kmeans||，用于 kmeans|| 的每次迭代中。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:59 of
msgid "Only work for kmeans||, indicates how may iterations required."
msgstr "仅适用于 kmeans||，表示需要多少次迭代。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:61 of
msgid "Whether or not to return the number of iterations."
msgstr "是否返回迭代次数。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.cluster.k_means.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:64 of
msgid ""
"* **centroid** (*float ndarray with shape (k, n_features)*) -- Centroids "
"found at the last iteration of k-means. * **label** (*integer ndarray "
"with shape (n_samples,)*) -- label[i] is the code or index of the "
"centroid the   i'th observation is closest to. * **inertia** (*float*) --"
" The final value of the inertia criterion (sum of squared distances to   "
"the closest centroid for all observations in the training set). * "
"**best_n_iter** (*int*) -- Number of iterations corresponding to the best"
" results.   Returned only if `return_n_iter` is set to True."
msgstr ""
"* **centroid** (*float ndarray with shape (k, n_features)*) -- 在 k-means"
" 最后一次迭代中找到的质心。\n"
"* **label** (*integer ndarray with shape (n_samples,)*) -- label[i] 是第 "
"i 个观测值最近的质心的代码或索引。\n"
"* **inertia** (*float*) -- 惯性准则的最终值（训练集中所有观测值到最近质心"
"的平方距离之和）。\n"
"* **best_n_iter** (*int*) -- 与最佳结果对应的迭代次数。仅当 `return_n_"
"iter` 设置为 True 时返回。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:64 of
msgid ""
"**centroid** (*float ndarray with shape (k, n_features)*) -- Centroids "
"found at the last iteration of k-means."
msgstr ""
"**centroid** (*float ndarray with shape (k, n_features)*) -- 在 k-means "
"最后一次迭代中找到的质心。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:65 of
msgid ""
"**label** (*integer ndarray with shape (n_samples,)*) -- label[i] is the "
"code or index of the centroid the i'th observation is closest to."
msgstr ""
"**label** (*integer ndarray with shape (n_samples,)*) -- label[i] 是第 i "
"个观测值最近的质心的代码或索引。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:67 of
msgid ""
"**inertia** (*float*) -- The final value of the inertia criterion (sum of"
" squared distances to the closest centroid for all observations in the "
"training set)."
msgstr ""
"**inertia** (*float*) -- 惯性准则的最终值（训练集中所有观测值到最近质心的"
"平方距离之和）。"

#: maxframe.learn.cluster._kmeans.k_means:69 of
msgid ""
"**best_n_iter** (*int*) -- Number of iterations corresponding to the best"
" results. Returned only if `return_n_iter` is set to True."
msgstr ""
"**best_n_iter** (*int*) -- 与最佳结果对应的迭代次数。仅当 `return_n_iter`"
" 设置为 True 时返回。"

